要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"d02bae189a2ad93fff72b9c421af69b49c042339","tid":1667204,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哦 明撚晒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fc9047e765e250fb214c57eca81d3898c8c79c","tid":1667204,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"今次清真寺事件真係令到港共亂哂章法<br />\n水炮車散仔你今次真係應記一功呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員會是必須</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b6bf779f5c12521d4c02a46a7e0ee5303a6ca5d","tid":1667204,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"5ec078b3e53b33980a7222d4e884aa5ffcf08334","tid":1667204,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"呢單野文宣組一定要大大力講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14b2180cc754be803e20f8b7e72e35dc401d3b8","tid":1667204,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fc9047e765e250fb214c57eca81d3898c8c79c","tid":1667204,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"今次清真寺事件真係令到港共亂哂章法<br />\n水炮車散仔你今次真係應記一功呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"colo